  "texts": [
    "BLEU [57], ROUGE [58] and METEOR [59] assess token overlap, evaluating the alignment of tokens in the explanation.",
    "On the other hand, SentBERT [60] and BERTScore [61] evaluate semantic similarity, assessing the closeness of meanings between the generated explanation and the references.",
    "Results and analysesIn this section, we present experimental results and analyze the performances of the TIP framework.",
    "We focus on understanding how different aspects of the framework contribute to its overall effectiveness in generating accurate commonsense explanations.",
    "Main resultsOur proposed TIP framework was evaluated on two commonsense explanation generation datasets: ComVE and our newly constructed CSE dataset."
  ]
